body:
Ready for another round of random conversations i have with my boyfriend about kpop?

Him: (Humming to himself)

Me: (Stares at him)

Him: (Not realising I’m staring) You gave me the best of me, so you give you the best of you.

Me: Did you just…?

Him: (Goes bright red) Shut up, its a good song. Whats it called again?

Me: Magic Shop

Him: (Immediately gets on his phone and downloads it on spotify)

😂😂😂😂

Hes becoming a fanboy! 🙌🙌

blog.description: D / 21 / student / Namjoon biased / I write scenarios for BTS/ Requests are OPEN/    Masterlist

body:
BTS TAG GAME

Tagged by: a friend on Instagram 💖

Rules: Answer the questions and tag more ARMY friends to play along

———————

1. First BTS Song?

-> FIRE

2. First bias?

-> Jungkook

3. Current Bias?

-> Namjoon 💖

4. Put the members in order of your bias list

-> Namjoon

-> Yoonmin

-> Tae, Jhope, Jungkook, Jin (in no particular order)

5. Favourite BTS Song?

-> There’s a lot but if I had to pick a number one it would probably be Spring Day or 2! 3!

6. Favourite BTS Song that is underrated?

-> Just one Day, Young Forever, For You

7. Favourite Song of Wings?

-> Outro: Wings, Lie

8. Favourite Song of each LY Her, Tear and Answer?

-> HER: Serendipity, Mic Drop

-> TEAR: Magic Shop, Anpanman, Fake Love

-> ANSWER: Epiphany, Answer:Love Yourself, Euphoria

9. Favourite Music Video?

-> They all have something special to them but I’d probably go with RUN

10. Favourite Dancer?

-> Depends on the dance really. If it’s more of a hip hop style - Jhope, and if it’s more slow and contemporary - Jimin

11. Favourite Vocalist?

-> Taehyung

12. Favourite Rapper?

-> No one will make me choose

13. Favourite hair color on each member?

-> Jimin: blond/brown, black, BLUE

-> Jhope: black, pink, red/dark orange

-> Jungkook: brown lol, RED

-> Namjoon: brown/dark blond, greyish, orange, PURPLE

-> Jin: Pink, Black

-> Taehyung & Yoongi: Taegi rocks every hair color let’s not argue

14. Favourite Choreography?

-> Not Today

15. Favourite Ship?

-> Vmin and Vkook but honestly I do love them all ❤

———————

Some questions were really hard to choose and answer for 🤐

I tag: Everyone that follows me! 💜 If you do decide to play along please tag me in your post so I can read your answers 😘

summary: Just a petty rant because Ive seen a few Hahah 😂😂look at tiny Jimin wearing his Massive Platform shoes on Twit and here and ......
body:
Just a petty rant because Ive seen a few Hahah 😂😂look at tiny Jimin wearing his Massive Platform shoes on Twit and here and … ugh why point it out like he’s the only one ? They’re nearly all wearing platforms or heels… do you want to take a closer look ? Here we go …

Kookie in 3 inch Platform shoes, Hobi in heels

Jimin with 3 inch Plaform shoes just like Jungkook, Namjoon in Heels

Jin - the only one with no platform, Yoongi, slight rise like 2 inches? Tae - heels like Hobi and Nams about 3 inches ? look at his the top of his foot, the angle it’s at, it’s like a high heel, like his foot must be at nearly 45 degree angle in the shoe

Ps I see no difference,Jimins actually look a bit lower …

Just a point I can’t see how they can dance with massive inserts and platforms so the best time to see their actual height is when they are doing dance training or concerts..otherwise they couldn’t do it, too clumpy.

I’m short and I hate not being able to reach the top of the shelf in stores so the short jokes just 😕it’s a pain in the neck ( literally ) in a world designed for tall people

And I’m petty

Let’s not even talk about cropped jeans being the right length for me I’m just 😳

Holes meant for knees half way down my shins

Yeah that
